{
  "stem": "12447.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the moment the German would pass that point and continue walking with his back toward me, my father would spread the wire, and I'd make my way through-- make my way through, hit another street, and get away.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was never caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somehow, the German never turned around to see me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And coming back, I could come through the gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would not stop me from coming through the gate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Whatever I carried, it was OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It, it wasn't really tight over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they would not let you out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was no way, if you did not have any papers, to go out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember my father, in the beginning, he had a paper to work on the Aryan side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was able to do some work in a-- in a German hospital as a plumber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had many friends in that town because he grew up over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for a while, he was able to, to work, which I used to go out of the ghetto and meet him over there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So sometimes, he would go to the-- to the kitchen and get some food for me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we kind of arranged things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had the papers to go out and come in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that ended also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How long did you stay in Sieldce for?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I stayed in Sieldce from this winter, 1941, until August of 1942, which was the end of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we lived in the ghetto by-- later on, in 1942-- by actually begging for food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my mother would go out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father would do the same thing for her what he did for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would open the wire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she would go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
